OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early cloud quickly
OL,6,Fbreaking up to leave a generally dry
OL,7,Fand bright day with plenty of sunny
OL,8,Fspells. An isolated light shower is
OL,9,Fpossible in the afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fvery warm and increasingly humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,13,Fdry night with clear spells and light
OL,14,Fwinds. Feeling warm and muggy,
OL,15,Fespecially in the east, bringing
OL,16,Fdifficult sleeping conditions.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
