OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA little showery rain is
OL,6,Fpossible through the morning, then
OL,7,Fturning drier and brighter with sunny
OL,8,Fspells into the afternoon. Feeling hot
OL,9,Fand humid for all.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FRemaining dry and sunny throughout the
OL,13,Fperiod. Feeling hot by day in the
OL,14,Fstrong sunshine and increasingly warm
OL,15,Fand humid overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
